descriptionHtml:
App’en til dig, der vil vide hvornår færgerne sejler, se de bedste priser og købe din billet i en fart.
Lav din personlige profil, så dit næste køb bliver lynhurtigt!

I denne app kan du:

- Købe billetter til MOLSLINJEN, BORNHOLMSLINJENs rute Ystad – Rønne, ALSLINJEN, LANGELANDSLINJEN eller SAMSØLINJEN, og se fartplanen for FANØLINJEN.
- Ændre dine billetter, hvis du bliver forhindret til din oprindelige afgang
- Gemme dit kreditkort, og booke endnu hurtigere fremover
- Se alle afgange og den billigste billet på samtlige afgange
- Få automatisk besked via app’en, hvis der sker ændringer på afgange, der er relevante for dig
- Oprette en profil så billetkøbet bliver endnu lettere
- Se samlet oversigt over dine købte billetter
- Tilføje billetter du har købt på MOLSLINJENs, BORNHOLMSLINJENs, ALSLINJENs, LANGELANDSLINJENs eller SAMSØLINJENs website, så du har dem med dig på farten
- Se hvilken færge, der sejler hvornår

Bemærk: Denne app kræver Android version 6 eller højere.

title: MOLSLINJEN

creator: Molslinjen A/S
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the new and improved MOLSLINJEN app!

We have rewritten the code and updated the design to give you an even faster and more reliable experience, allowing you to book your preferred ferry crossing in just a few seconds!

With the new update, you can see how long it should take you to drive to the ferry. So, there’ll be no doubt about which crossing suits you best. It’s also easier now to manage saved payment cards and add, for instance, a trailer to your booking. Passengers crossing Kattegat can also book business trips directly in the app, and visitors to Fanø can see how long we expect the queue to be at the ferry.

We will continually add new features to the app, and we look forward to welcoming you on board – both on our ferries and in the new app.

Kombardo!


The app with all our ferry departures and the best prices, and where you can buy your
ticket in seconds.

Create your own personal profile so you can buy your next ticket in seconds!
In this app, you can:
· Buy tickets for MOLSLINJEN, BORNHOLMSLINJEN’s route from Ystad to Rønne,
ALSLINJEN, LANGELANDSLINJEN and SAMSØLINJEN and see the timetable for
FANØLINJEN
· Change your tickets if you can’t make it to your original departure
· Save your payment card to make ticket purchase quicker next time
· See all departures and the cheapest ticket on each crossing
· Request an automatic message via the app if there are changes to any departures
relevant for you
· Create a profile to make ticket purchase even easier
· View a summary of the tickets you have purchased
· Add tickets you have bought via MOLSLINJEN’s, BORNHOLMSLINJEN’s, ALSLINJEN’s,
LANGELANDSLINJEN’s or SAMSØLINJEN’s website so that you always have them with
you
· See which ferries are sailing and when
descriptionShort: All our ferry departures and where you can buy your ticket in seconds.

descriptionHtml:
Welcome to your new and improved MOLSLINJEN app!

Update:
The biggest change you will notice is our beautiful new redesign. In addition, we have added ForSea, which is our new route between Helsingør and Helsingborg.

You can still do everything that you’re used to doing in the MOLSLINJEN app. The app’s many features are listed below.

In the MOLSLINJEN app, you can:
• see the timetable and book tickets for all our routes: MOLSLINJEN, BORNHOLMSLINJEN, ALSLINJEN, LANGELANDSLINJEN, SAMSØLINJEN, FANØLINJEN and ForSea.
• create a profile and add, for example, travelling companions, vehicles and payment cards.
• see a complete overview of your tickets.
• add trip card and commuter agreement.
• skip the queue and pre-order food and drinks for MOLSLINJEN on the Aarhus-Odden route.
• see your expected driving time to selected ferry ports.
• change your ticket if you are unable to make your original departure.
• receive automatic notifications via the app if changes are made to any relevant departures.
• add tickets you have purchased on the MOLSLINJEN, BORNHOLMSLINJEN, ALSLINJEN, LANGELANDSLINJEN, SAMSØLINJEN, FANØLINJEN and ForSea websites so you have them with you on the go.

The app will continually be updated with new features.
We look forward to welcoming you on board – both on the ferries and in the new app.
Kombardo!

Please note: This Android app requires min. software version 7.
